 *   CC_CONNECT_BASE_URL        默认 http://127.0.0.1:9820
 *   CC_CONNECT_TOKEN           cc-connect Management API token(必填)
 *   CC_CONNECT_BRIDGE_URL      默认 ws://127.0.0.1:9810/bridge/ws
 *   CC_CONNECT_BRIDGE_TOKEN    cc-connect Bridge token(必填)
